      <title>JetThoughts Thailand Trip</title>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Wouldn&amp;#39;t it be great to wake up on a February morning to the sound of waves lapping and birds singing, have some fragrant fried rice with seafood and a cold mango shake for breakfast, go for a swim in the azure-blue sea, then open your laptop and start coding? Sure, it would be awesome! That&amp;#39;s what we thought and decided to swap our nasty Ukrainian winter for a quite tolerable tropical one. &lt;/p&gt;

